          <div class="govspeak">
<p>Letter from the Culture Secretary, Oliver Dowden, to the BBC and S4C, requesting specific financial information, as required under the BBCâ€™s Royal Charter, to begin the process to agree the appropriate level of the licence fee from 2022 and to ensure a settlement which offers the best value for money for licence fee payers.</p>
